        {
            "key": "020",
            "text": "but she didn’t let me",
            "audio": "en_020.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "021",
            "text": "Then we talked about",
            "audio": "en_021.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "022",
            "text": "how to manage our money better in the future",
            "audio": "en_022.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "023",
            "text": "Later, we went into a few shops",
            "audio": "en_023.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "024",
            "text": "I wanted to buy new shoes,",
            "audio": "en_024.mp3"
