            "text": "but they were far more expensive than I expected",
            "audio": "en_025.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "026",
            "text": "So I decided to wait",
            "audio": "en_026.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "027",
            "text": "and try to save up some money first",
            "audio": "en_027.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "028",
            "text": "On our way home,",
            "audio": "en_028.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "029",
            "text": "we walked along the river",
            "audio": "en_029.mp3"
        },
        {
            "key": "030",
